data.description: Upgraded house in desirable Salem Village neighborhood! Living area w/ hardwood floors, fireplace, built-ins. Half-bath on the lower level for guests. Spacious master downstairs with master bathroom; upstairs features two bedrooms, a full bath, and a balcony off of front bedroom. The house has a Vivint security system, Nest programmable thermostat, the downstairs A/C unit was replaced last August, and the side yard is fenced. Community pool & playground, walking distance to Holcomb Elementary & Holt Middle.
